Package com.gcu.agms.repository.impl

Class JdbcFlightRepository

java.lang.Object
com.gcu.agms.repository.impl.JdbcFlightRepository
All Implemented Interfaces:
FlightRepository
@Repository public class JdbcFlightRepository extends Object implements FlightRepository
JDBC implementation of the FlightRepository interface. This class handles data access operations for flights using Spring JDBC.
